porting Events in 2021<\/a><ul class=\"ez-toc-list-level-3\"><li class=\"ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-10\" href=\"https:\/\/www.roadtrips.com\/blog\/the-best-usa-sporting-events-for-2021\/#MLB_AllStar_Game\" title=\"MLB All-Star Game\">MLB All-Star Game<\/a><\/li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-11\" href=\"https:\/\/www.roadtrips.com\/blog\/the-best-usa-sporting-events-for-2021\/#PGA_Championship\" title=\"PGA Championship\">PGA Championship<\/a><\/li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-12\" href=\"https:\/\/www.roadtrips.com\/blog\/the-best-usa-sporting-events-for-2021\/#US_Open_Golf\" title=\"US Open Golf\">US Open Golf<\/a><\/li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-13\" href=\"https:\/\/www.roadtrips.com\/blog\/the-best-usa-sporting-events-for-2021\/#World_Series\" title=\"World Series\">World Series<\/a><\/li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-14\" href=\"https:\/\/www.roadtrips.com\/blog\/the-best-usa-sporting-events-for-2021\/#Rose_Bowl\" title=\"Rose Bowl\">Rose Bowl<\/a><\/li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-15\" href=\"https:\/\/www.roadtrips.com\/blog\/the-best-usa-sporting-events-for-2021\/#Final_Four\" title=\"Final Four\">Final Four<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_Major_Sporting_Events_in_the_USA_for_2021\"><\/span><strong>The Major Sporting Events in the USA for 2021<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Super_Bowl\"><\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.roadtrips.com\/football-packages\/super-bowl\/\"><strong>Super Bowl<\/strong><\/a><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignright wp-image-34114 size-medium\" src=\"https:\/\/www.roadtrips.com\/wp-c