/p>\n<p><!--HubSpot Call-to-Action Code --><span id=\"hs-cta-wrapper-f87cd221-2720-442b-a7b5-1ba4d9dcf998\" class=\"hs-cta-wrapper\"><span id=\"hs-cta-f87cd221-2720-442b-a7b5-1ba4d9dcf998\" class=\"hs-cta-node hs-cta-f87cd221-2720-442b-a7b5-1ba4d9dcf998\"><!-- [if lte IE 8]>\n\n\n<div id=\"hs-cta-ie-element\"><\/div>\n\n\n<![endif]--><a href=\"https:\/\/cta-redirect.hubspot.com\/cta\/redirect\/2166909\/f87cd221-2720-442b-a7b5-1ba4d9dcf998\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img id=\"hs-cta-img-f87cd221-2720-442b-a7b5-1ba4d9dcf998\" class=\"hs-cta-img\" style=\"border-width: 0px;\" src=\"https:\/\/no-cache.hubspot.com\/cta\/default\/2166909\/f87cd221-2720-442b-a7b5-1ba4d9dcf998.png\" alt=\"Download a Super Bowl Brochure\" \/><\/a><\/span><br \/>\n<\/span><!-- end HubSpot Call-to-Action Code --><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Daytona_500\"><\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.roadtrips.com\/auto-racing-packages\/daytona-500\/\"><strong>Daytona 500<img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-17370 alignright\" src=\"https:\/\/www.roadtrips.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/daytona500-hero2-300x166.jpg\" alt=\"daytona 500 packages\" width=\"300\" height=\"166\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.roadtrips.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/daytona500-hero2-300x166.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.roadtrips.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/daytona500-hero2-768x425.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.roadtrips.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/daytona500-hero2-1024x567.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.roadtrips.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/daytona500-hero2.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/strong><\/a><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<h4><em>February 12-15, 2021 <\/em><br \/>\n<em>Daytona, Florida<\/em><\/h4>\n<p><script type=\"application\/ld+json\">\n{\n  \"@context\": \"http:\/\/schema.org\/\",\n  \"@type\": \"SportsEvent\",\n  \"name\": \"Daytona 500\",\n  \"startDate\": \"2021-02-12\",\n  \"endDate\": \"2021-02-15\",\n  \"location\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Place\",\n    \"name\": \"Daytona International Speedway\",\n    \"address\": {\n      \"addressLocality\": \"Daytona\",\n      \"addressRegion\": \"Florida\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n<\/script><br \/>\nA highlight of every February is the Daytona 500, NASCAR\u2019s premier event. Florida is a perfect destination for a mid-winter getaway and getting to experience one of the biggest car races in the United States at the same time makes it that much better. The <a href=\"https:\/\/www.roadtrips.com\/luxury-travel-guides\/daytona-500-guide\/\">Daytona International Speedway<\/a>, which hosts the event, offers an incredible fan experience, even more so after its massive \u201cDaytona Rising\u201d renovation.<\/p>\n<p><!--HubSpot Call-to-Action Code --><span id=\"hs-cta-wrapper-289dbc8e-2847-4a98-b6b5-c6828a03c4c8\" class=\"hs-cta-wrapper\"><span id=\"hs-cta-289dbc8e-2847-4a98-b6b5-c6828a03c4c8\" class=\"hs-cta-node hs-cta-289dbc8e-2847-4a98-b6b5-c6828a03c4c8\"><!-- [if lte IE 8]>\n\n\n<div id=\"hs-cta-ie-element\"><\/div>\n\n\n<![endif]--><a href=\"https:\/\/cta-redirect.hubspot.com\/cta\/redirect\/2166909\/289dbc8e-2847-4a98-b6b5-c6828a03c4c8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img id=\"hs-cta-img-289dbc8e-2847-4a98-b6b5-c6828a03c4c8\" class=\"hs-cta-img\" style=\"border-width: 0px;\" src=\"https:\/\/no-cache.hubspot.com\/cta\/default\/2166909\/289dbc8e-2847-4a98-b6b5-c6828a03c4c8.png\" alt=\"FREE 2021 Daytona 500 Brochure\" \/><\/a><\/span><br \/>\n<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_Masters\"><\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.roadtrips.com\/professional-golf-packages\/masters\/\"><strong>The Masters<img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignright wp-image-32788 size-medium\" src=\"https:\/\/www.roadtrips.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/masters-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"masters golf packages\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.roadtrips.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/masters-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.roadtrips.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/masters.jpg 400w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/strong><\/a><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<h4><em>April 5-11, 2021<\/em><br \/>\n<em>Augusta, Georgia<\/em><\/h4>\n<p><script type=\"application\/ld+json\">\n{\n  \"@context\": \"http:\/\/schema.org\/\",\n  \"@type\": \"SportsEvent\",\n  \"name\": \"Masters Golf Tournament\",\n  \"startDate\": \"2021-11-09\",\n  \"endDate\": \"2021-11-15\",\n  \"location\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Place\",\n    \"name\": \"Augusta National Golf Club\",\n    \"address\": {\n      \"addressLocality\": \"Augusta\",\n      \"addressRegion\": \"Georgia\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n<\/script><br \/>\nThe Masters is not only one of the top sporting events in the US, it\u2019s widely considered to be the <a href=\"https:\/\/bleacherreport.com\/articles\/1415728-ranking-the-10-tournaments-every-hardcore-golf-fan-needs-to-attend\">best golf tournament to attend.<\/a> It\u2019s a true bucket list event for those that are passionate about golf. Watching the tournament on television is a thrill, but attending the event in person is a totally different experience. When you walk the hallowed grounds of Augusta National Golf Club you get a sense of the course that the cameras just cannot capture. And to feel the atmosphere during Masters week \u2026\u00a0 there\u2019s simply nothing like it.<\/p>\n<p><!--HubSpot Call-to-Action Code --><span id=\"hs-cta-wrapper-21163db4-021a-48bd-988b-8cbe58dd1729\" class=\"hs-cta-wrapper\"><span id=\"hs-cta-21163db4-021a-48bd-988b-8cbe58dd1729\" class=\"hs-cta-node hs-cta-21163db4-021a-48bd-988b-8cbe58dd1729\"><!-- [if lte IE 8]>\n\n\n<div id=\"hs-cta-ie-element\"><\/div>\n\n\n<![endif]--><a href=\"https:\/\/cta-redirect.hubspot.com\/cta\/redirect\/2166909\/21163db4-021a-48bd-988b-8cbe58dd1729\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img id=\"hs-cta-img-21163db4-021a-48bd-988b-8cbe58dd1729\" class=\"hs-cta-img\" style=\"border-width: 0px;\" src=\"https:\/\/no-cache.hubspot.com\/cta\/default\/2166909\/21163db4-021a-48bd-988b-8cbe58dd1729.png\" alt=\"FREE 2021 Masters Brochure\" \/><\/a><\/span><br \/>\n<\/span><!-- end HubSpot Call-to-Action Code --><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Kentucky_Derby\"><\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.roadtrips.com\/horse-racing-packages\/kentucky-derby\/\"><strong>Kentucky Derby<img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignright wp-image-33150 size-medium\" src=\"https:\/\/www.roadtrips.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/kentucky-derby-300x166.jpg\" alt=\"Kentucky Derby packages\" width=\"300\" height=\"166\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.roadtrips.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/kentucky-derby-300x166.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.roadtrips.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/kentucky-derby-1024x567.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.roadtrips.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/kentucky-derby-768x425.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.roadtrips.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/kentucky-derby-1536x850.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/www.roadtrips.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/kentucky-derby.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/www.roadtrips.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/kentucky-derby-960x532.jpg 960w, https:\/\/www.roadtrips.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/kentucky-derby-640x354.jpg 640w, https:\/\/www.roadtrips.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/kentucky-derby-480x266.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/strong><\/a><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<h4><em>April 29 \u2013 May 2, 2021<\/em><br \/>\n<em>Louisville, Kentucky<\/em><\/h4>\n<p><script type=\"application\/ld+json\">\n{\n  \"@context\": \"http:\/\/schema.org\/\",\n  \"@type\": \"SportsEvent\",\n  \"name\": \"Kentucky Derby\",\n  \"startDate\": \"2021-04-29\",\n  \"endDate\": \"2021-05-02\",\n  \"location\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Place\",\n    \"name\": \"Churchill Downs\",\n    \"address\": {\n      \"addressLocality\": \"Louisville\",\n      \"addressRegion\": \"Kentucky\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n<\/script><br \/>\nThe Kentucky Derby is so much more than a thrilling day of horse races. It has all the buzz of a major sporting event plus fashion, tradition, and celebrity. It\u2019s such a fun event and the festivities go on all week long.\u00a0 As the first leg of horse racing\u2019s Triple Crown (followed by the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.roadtrips.com\/horse-racing-packages\/preakness-stakes\/\">Preakness Stakes<\/a>, and the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.roadtrips.com\/horse-racing-packages\/belmont-stakes\/\">Belmont Stakes<\/a>), there\u2019s a lot on the line and the excitement is high.<\/p>\n<p><!--HubSpot Call-to-Action Code --><span id=\"hs-cta-wrapper-13ac783f-dc17-4458-abc8-e95e1948ab57\" class=\"hs-cta-wrapper\"><span id=\"hs-cta-13ac783f-dc17-4458-abc8-e95e1948ab57\" class=\"hs-cta-node hs-cta-13ac783f-dc17-4458-abc8-e95e1948ab57\"><!-- [if lte IE 8]>\n\n\n<div id=\"hs-cta-ie-element\"><\/div>\n\n\n<![endif]--><a href=\"https:\/\/cta-redirect.hubspot.com\/cta\/redirect\/2166909\/13ac783f-dc17-4458-abc8-e95e1948ab57\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img id=\"hs-cta-img-13ac783f-dc17-4458-abc8-e95e1948ab57\" class=\"hs-cta-img\" style=\"border-width: 0px;\" src=\"https:\/\/no-cache.hubspot.com\/cta\/default\/2166909\/13ac783f-dc17-4458-abc8-e95e1948ab57.png\" alt=\"FREE 2021 Kentucky Derby Brochure\" \/><\/a><\/span><br \/>\n<\/span><!-- end HubSpot Call-to-Action Code --><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Indianapolis_500\"><\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.roadtrips.com\/auto-racing-packages\/indy-500\/\"><strong>Indianapolis 500<img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignright wp-image-22814 size-medium\" src=\"https:\/\/www.roadtrips.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/half-indy-500-300x150.jpg\" alt=\"Indianapolis 500 packages\" width=\"300\" height=\"150\" \/><\/strong><\/a><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<h4><em>May 28-31, 2021 <\/em><br \/>\n<em>Indianapolis, Indiana<\/em><\/h4>\n<p><script type=\"application\/ld+json\">\n{\n  \"@context\": \"http:\/\/schema.org\/\",\n  \"@type\": \"SportsEvent\",\n  \"name\": \"Indianapolis 500\",\n  \"startDate\": \"2021-05-28\",\n  \"endDate\": \"2021-05-31\",\n  \"location\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Place\",\n    \"name\": \"Indianapolis Motor Speedway\",\n    \"address\": {\n      \"addressLocality\": \"Indianapolis\",\n      \"addressRegion\": \"Indiana\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n<\/script><br \/>\nDubbed \u201c<a href=\"https:\/\/www.cnn.com\/2013\/09\/06\/us\/indianapolis-500-fast-facts\/index.html\">The Biggest Spectacle in Racing<\/a>,\u201d the Indy 500 (usually) takes place every spring at Indianapolis Motor Speedway. It\u2019s the largest single day sporting event in the United States and has a long history, dating back over a century.\u00a0 The 2021 Indy 500 will mark the 105<sup>th<\/sup> running of this popular major sporting event and also a return to its traditional Memorial Day Weekend date after the 2020 race was rescheduled due to COVID-19.<\/p>\n<p><!--HubSpot Call-to-Action Code --><span id=\"hs-cta-wrapper-367e28aa-a335-42c8-9f47-72ac0a8283b7\" class=\"hs-cta-wrapper\"><span id=\"hs-cta-367e28aa-a335-42c8-9f47-72ac0a8283b7\" class=\"hs-cta-node hs-cta-367e28aa-a335-42c8-9f47-72ac0a8283b7\"><!-- [if lte IE 8]>\n\n\n<div id=\"hs-cta-ie-element\"><\/div>\n\n\n<![endif]--><a href=\"https:\/\/cta-redirect.hubspot.com\/cta\/redirect\/2166909\/367e28aa-a335-42c8-9f47-72ac0a8283b7\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img id=\"hs-cta-img-367e28aa-a335-42c8-9f47-72ac0a8283b7\" class=\"hs-cta-img\" style=\"border-width: 0px;\" src=\"https:\/\/no-cache.hubspot.com\/cta\/default\/2166909\/367e28aa-a335-42c8-9f47-72ac0a8283b7.png\" alt=\"Download Our FREE Indianapolis Travel Guide\" \/><\/a><\/span><br \/>\n<\/span><!-- end HubSpot Call-to-Action Code --><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"US_Open_Tennis\"><\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.roadtrips.com\/tennis-packages\/us-open-tennis\/\"><strong>US Open Tennis<img loading=\"lazy\